bangida. February 17, 2018 In "News" Barely 24 hours after former Military President, General Ibrahim Babangida (retd) endorsed Social Democratic Party, SDP, for next year’s general elections,  National Working Committee, NWC, of People Democratic Party, PDP, Monday visited him in his Hilltop Mansion, in Minna, Niger State. April 16, 2018 In "News" This is the story of how the National Chairman of People’s Democratic Party, PDP, Alhaji Bamanga Tukur, who operates from the Wadata Plaza, Wuse Zone 5, carry out his activities daily, with a cursory look at his actions after the August 31 Special National Convention of the party where the… September 15, 2013 In "Politics"